  "detailed_description": "<strong>This is a nostalgic game, but it brings new mechanics, with new possibilities and experiences.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREE MOVEMENT:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will not be limited to 90 degree angles.</li></ul> <i>(How about making smooth turns or even rotating on your own axis? This can be very useful during combat.)</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/fdf2afcd6272c663a78004d3e6d5997a.poster.avif?t=1708651965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/fdf2afcd6272c663a78004d3e6d5997a.webm?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/fdf2afcd6272c663a78004d3e6d5997a.mp4?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Back up your tank.</li></ul> <i>(In combat, backing up doesn't always mean running away, okay?</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/7c3990424708fc8697b6f7101b60e5f1.poster.avif?t=1708651965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/7c3990424708fc8697b6f7101b60e5f1.webm?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/7c3990424708fc8697b6f7101b60e5f1.mp4?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect shields to activate them in the future,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot the explosives to detonate them.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/bd53b37a2be138025711745f9a3382a8.poster.avif?t=1708651965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/bd53b37a2be138025711745f9a3382a8.webm?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/bd53b37a2be138025711745f9a3382a8.mp4?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After defeating all the tank artillery, to pass the level, you still have to face a tough and clever big boss.</li></ul><i>(Don't let him get you!).</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In each level the game will become more challenging.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenge yourself in the more than 20 levels contained in War Tank combat.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>This is a nostalgic game, but it brings new mechanics, with new possibilities and experiences.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREE MOVEMENT:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will not be limited to 90 degree angles.</li></ul> <i>(How about making smooth turns or even rotating on your own axis? This can be very useful during combat.)</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/fdf2afcd6272c663a78004d3e6d5997a.poster.avif?t=1708651965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/fdf2afcd6272c663a78004d3e6d5997a.webm?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/fdf2afcd6272c663a78004d3e6d5997a.mp4?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Back up your tank.</li></ul> <i>(In combat, backing up doesn't always mean running away, okay?</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/7c3990424708fc8697b6f7101b60e5f1.poster.avif?t=1708651965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/7c3990424708fc8697b6f7101b60e5f1.webm?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1567930/extras/7c3990424708fc8697b6f7101b60e5f1.mp4?t=1708651965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect shields to activate them in the future,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot the explosives to detonate them.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:/